      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To confirm the jurisdiction of the Consumer Product Safety Commission with respect to releasing systems on residential window bars and to establish a consumer product safety standard ensuring that all such bars include a quick-release mechanism.</title>
